						               													<description>Doomtown: Reloaded &amp;ndash; There Comes a Reckoning is an expansion for the Doomtown: Reloaded expandable card game.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;This expansion includes a revamped rulebook and the new Legend card type featuring the Servitors, the biggest badasses of the Deadlands universe!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;This expansion includes 96 NEW cards for the Doomtown: Reloaded Expandable Card Game. There are four copies each of 24 unique cards to expand your play experience.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The new cards add support for all six factions as well as themes such as Blessed and Gadgets.  It's also the first set to introduce a new card type&amp;mdash;Legends!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Legends represent the most badass and influential figures the Weird West has to offer.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;There Comes a Reckoning also introduces key elements of the greater Deadlands setting and features stunning art from the industry's best artists.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The Servitors are the most powerful adversaries the Weird West has to offer, second only to their masters, the Reckoners&amp;ndash;otherwise known as the Four Horsemen of the Apocalypse!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Now YOU can harness the power of  Ezekiah Grimme (Famine), Raven (War), Darius Hellstromme (Pestilence), or Jasper Stone (Death).&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Legends trade starting wealth in exchange for power. You now have the option to attach a Servitor to your Outfit&amp;rsquo;s home in order to enable far-reaching strategies. Keep in mind though that evil in Deadlands is always a choice, and always comes with a price!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
